title: Advanced Study Program - MIT Employee Open House
summary:
MIT Professional Education’s Advanced Study Program (ASP) offers working professionals or qualified students the opportunity to study at MIT as non-degree students—either part time or full time—for a semester, year, or longer. 
Wondering if the ASP is right for you? Join us for our Virtual Open House on April 25.
